# Cloudflare Pages redirects → jsDelivr CDN for the big asset dirs (#218, #335).
#
# Pinned to an IMMUTABLE er-assets commit (NOT @main). jsDelivr caches a mutable
# `@main` ref at its edge + in the browser for ~7 days, so when an atlas/icon
# sheet is updated, players keep the OLD (wrong) cached sprite for days — that's
# the "Psyduck icon = Mega Charizard X" / "Redux Rattata = Mega Zard X" stale-
# sprite class. An immutable `@<sha>` ref is served correctly and the URL CHANGES
# on every asset update, so a bump here is a guaranteed cache-bust for everyone
# (and `_redirects` itself is served no-cache, so the new URLs propagate at once).
#
# 🔁 WHEN er-assets CHANGES: bump the SHA below to the new Heraklines/er-assets
#    HEAD (`gh api repos/Heraklines/er-assets/commits/main --jq .sha`) and redeploy.
#    Forgetting to bump = players won't see the new assets (but never a stale mix).
